    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>I believe they are refactoring from <code>junit.framework</code> to <code>org.junit</code> and <code>junit.framework.Assert</code> is maintained for backwards compatibility. </p>\n"
  }, {
