      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "This answer is not entirely correct, you can make static imports of methods in  the class junit.framework.Assert  and org.junit.Assert. It is, however, probably a good idea to stick to the org.junit.Assert class  since it is newer , slightly rewritten and probably meant as a replacement."
